<!DOCTYPE html>
<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><title>HRGoTo HCM - System Test Guide</title>
<style>
body { font-family: Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 40px 60px; color: #1a202c; }
h1 { color: #162C5B; font-size: 28pt; margin-bottom: 0; }
h2 { color: #2B6CB0; font-size: 20pt; margin-top: 0; font-weight: normal; }
h3 { color: #162C5B; font-size: 14pt; margin-top: 28px; margin-bottom: 10px; border-bottom: 2px solid #CBD5E0; padding-bottom: 4px; }
.subtitle { color: #718096; font-size: 12pt; margin-bottom: 30px; }
hr { border: none; border-top: 1.5px solid #CBD5E0; margin: 20px 0; }
table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 10px 0 25px 0; font-size: 9.5pt; }
th { background-color: #162C5B; color: white; padding: 7px 8px; text-align: left; font-size: 9pt; }
td { padding: 6px 8px; border: 0.5pt solid #CBD5E0; vertical-align: top; }
tr:nth-child(even) { background-color: #F7FAFC; }
.num { width: 40px; text-align: center; white-space: nowrap; }
.pf { width: 70px; text-align: center; font-size: 12pt; }
.prep { background: #EBF8FF; padding: 15px 20px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 15px 0; border-left: 4px solid #2B6CB0; }
.prep h4 { margin: 0 0 8px 0; color: #2B6CB0; }
.prep ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; }
.prep li { margin-bottom: 4px; }
.flow { background: #F0FFF4; padding: 15px 20px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 15px 0; border-left: 4px solid #2F855A; }
.flow h4 { margin: 0 0 8px 0; color: #2F855A; }
.flow ol { margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; }
.flow li { margin-bottom: 4px; }
.signoff { margin-top: 40px; }
.signoff td { border: none; padding: 8px 30px 8px 0; background: none; font-size: 11pt; }
.prereq { background: #F0FFF4; }
.prereq th { background-color: #2F855A; }
</style></head>
<body>

<h1>HRGoTo HCM</h1>
<h2>System-Wide Test Guide</h2>
<p class="subtitle">Comprehensive Component-by-Component Testing Before Demonstration</p>
<hr>

<div class="prep">
<h4>Preparation</h4>
<ul>
<li>Open browser in <strong>incognito/private window</strong> to avoid cached sessions.</li>
<li>Have <strong>4 test accounts</strong> ready: Super Admin, HR Manager, Supervisor, Staff.</li>
<li>Open browser DevTools (<strong>F12</strong>) → <strong>Console tab</strong> to catch JavaScript errors.</li>
<li>Have sample files ready: JPEG avatar (&lt;2MB), PDF document (&lt;5MB).</li>
<li>Keep this guide open and mark <strong>Pass/Fail</strong> for each test case.</li>
</ul>
</div>

<div class="flow">
<h4>Recommended Test Order (Logical Workflow)</h4>
<ol>
<li><strong>Login</strong> as Super Admin →</li>
<li><strong>Configure</strong> the system first: Departments → Designations → Ranks → Roles → Users → Appraisal Metrics → Company Profile → ID Card →</li>
<li><strong>Onboard</strong> staff (needs departments, designations, ranks, users configured) →</li>
<li><strong>Recruitment</strong> (needs departments, designations, jobs configured) →</li>
<li>Dashboard, Staff Registry, Self-Service, Approvals, Leave, Appraisals, Promotions, Attendance, Payroll, Communications</li>
</ol>
</div>

<p><strong>Total Test Cases:</strong> 129 &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Components:</strong> 17</p>
<hr>
<h3>Component 1: Authentication & Session Management</h3><table><tr><th class="num">#</th><th style="width:260px">Test Case</th><th>Steps</th><th style="width:280px">Expected Result</th><th class="pf">Pass/Fail</th></tr><tr><td class="num">1.1</td><td><strong>Login page loads</strong></td><td>Navigate to /login</td><td>Clean login form, no console errors</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">1.2</td><td><strong>Valid login (Super Admin)</strong></td><td>Enter Super Admin credentials</td><td>Redirect to /dashboard, notification bell, user name in top-right</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">1.3</td><td><strong>Invalid login</strong></td><td>Enter wrong password</td><td>Error message, no redirect</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">1.4</td><td><strong>Session timeout modal</strong></td><td>Stay idle 25 minutes</td><td>Modal "Session Expiring Soon" centered on screen</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">1.5</td><td><strong>Stay logged in</strong></td><td>Click "Stay Logged In"</td><td>Modal dismissed, session reset</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">1.6</td><td><strong>Auto-logout</strong></td><td>Stay idle 30 min total</td><td>Redirected to /logout</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">1.7</td><td><strong>Logout</strong></td><td>Profile menu → Logout</td><td>Redirected to /login, cannot access /dashboard</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">1.8</td><td><strong>Forgot password</strong></td><td>Click "Forgot Password", enter email</td><td>Success message: reset link sent</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">1.9</td><td><strong>Role-based access</strong></td><td>Login as Staff, try /admin/users</td><td>403 Access denied or redirect</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr></table><h3>Component 2: Admin & System Configuration (Prerequisite)</h3><table><tr><th class="num">#</th><th style="width:260px">Test Case</th><th>Steps</th><th style="width:280px">Expected Result</th><th class="pf">Pass/Fail</th></tr><tr><td class="num">2.1</td><td><strong>Departments CRUD</strong></td><td>Navigate to /admin/departments</td><td>Create, edit, and delete departments. New department appears in dropdowns</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">2.2</td><td><strong>Designations CRUD</strong></td><td>Navigate to /admin/designations</td><td>Create, edit, and delete designations. New designation appears in dropdowns</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">2.3</td><td><strong>Ranks with leave_days</strong></td><td>Navigate to /admin/ranks</td><td>CRUD including leave_days field; value used in leave entitlement calculation</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">2.4</td><td><strong>Roles & permissions</strong></td><td>Navigate to /admin/roles-permissions</td><td>Role list with permission editor; changes affect access control</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">2.5</td><td><strong>User management</strong></td><td>Navigate to /admin/users</td><td>User table with Edit and Toggle Status; create initial user accounts</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">2.6</td><td><strong>Edit user role/status</strong></td><td>Click Edit on a user row</td><td>Modal with role dropdown and status toggle</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">2.7</td><td><strong>Toggle user active/inactive</strong></td><td>Click Toggle Status</td><td>User activated or deactivated immediately</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">2.8</td><td><strong>Appraisal metrics CRUD</strong></td><td>Navigate to /admin/appraisal-metrics</td><td>Create scoring metrics used in performance appraisals</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">2.9</td><td><strong>Company profile</strong></td><td>Navigate to /admin/company-profile</td><td>Edit organisation name, logo, address, contact info</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">2.10</td><td><strong>ID card configuration</strong></td><td>Navigate to /admin/id-card-config</td><td>Configure card layout, colours, fields, logo position</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">2.11</td><td><strong>Audit logs viewer</strong></td><td>Navigate to /admin/audit-logs</td><td>DataTable of all system actions, searchable and sortable</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">2.12</td><td><strong>Backup system</strong></td><td>Navigate to /admin/backup</td><td>Create DB backup, create files backup, download, delete</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">2.13</td><td><strong>ID card preview</strong></td><td>Navigate to /staff/id-card?id=X</td><td>ID card renders with staff photo + configuration applied</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">2.14</td><td><strong>ID card print</strong></td><td>Click Print on ID card</td><td>Browser print dialog opens</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr></table><h3>Component 3: Staff Onboarding (Multi-Step Wizard)</h3><table><tr><th class="num">#</th><th style="width:260px">Test Case</th><th>Steps</th><th style="width:280px">Expected Result</th><th class="pf">Pass/Fail</th></tr><tr><td class="num">3.1</td><td><strong>Wizard loads</strong></td><td>Login as Admin/HR, navigate to /onboard</td><td>4-step wizard: User Account → Personal Bio → Education → Experience</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">3.2</td><td><strong>Step navigation</strong></td><td>Click Next and Back through all steps</td><td>Sections show/hide correctly, current step highlighted</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">3.3</td><td><strong>Mandatory fields (Step 1)</strong></td><td>Leave surname empty, click Next</td><td>Error: "Mandatory parameter missing: [surname]"</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">3.4</td><td><strong>Mandatory fields (Step 2)</strong></td><td>Skip avatar upload</td><td>Error: "Staff Identity passport photo is required"</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">3.5</td><td><strong>Mandatory file (Step 3)</strong></td><td>Add institution, skip file upload</td><td>Error: "document file missing for Row #1"</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">3.6</td><td><strong>Avatar validation</strong></td><td>Upload >2MB or non-JPEG/PNG</td><td>Error: "Invalid image format or exceeds 2MB"</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">3.7</td><td><strong>Education file validation</strong></td><td>Upload >5MB or wrong format</td><td>Error: "must be valid PDF, JPEG, or PNG under 5MB"</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">3.8</td><td><strong>Duplicate email/username</strong></td><td>Use existing email or username</td><td>Error: "Identity conflict anomaly"</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">3.9</td><td><strong>Full successful submission</strong></td><td>Complete all 4 steps with valid data, click "Commit & Finalize"</td><td>Progress modal with bar + percentage → success → redirect to dashboard</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">3.10</td><td><strong>New staff in registry</strong></td><td>Navigate to /staff</td><td>Newly onboarded staff visible in directory table</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">3.11</td><td><strong>Notification sent</strong></td><td>Check bell notifications (other admin users)</td><td>Notification: "New Staff Onboarded" created for Super Admin + HR roles</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr></table><h3>Component 4: Recruitment & Hiring Pipeline</h3><table><tr><th class="num">#</th><th style="width:260px">Test Case</th><th>Steps</th><th style="width:280px">Expected Result</th><th class="pf">Pass/Fail</th></tr><tr><td class="num">4.1</td><td><strong>Recruitment dashboard</strong></td><td>Navigate to /recruitment</td><td>Stats cards: active jobs, total applicants, pipeline stages</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">4.2</td><td><strong>Jobs list</strong></td><td>Navigate to /recruitment/jobs</td><td>CRUD table with all job postings</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">4.3</td><td><strong>Create job posting</strong></td><td>Fill job title, description, status; submit</td><td>Job created, visible in list</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">4.4</td><td><strong>View applicants</strong></td><td>Click a job on recruitment dashboard</td><td>Applicant list for that specific job</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">4.5</td><td><strong>Update applicant status</strong></td><td>Click update-status on an applicant</td><td>Status changed, logged in history trail</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">4.6</td><td><strong>Kanban pipeline view</strong></td><td>Navigate to /recruitment/pipeline</td><td>Columns: Applied, Shortlisted, Interviewed, Offered, Hired, Rejected</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">4.7</td><td><strong>Move applicant in pipeline</strong></td><td>Click move on an applicant card</td><td>Applicant advances to next pipeline stage</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">4.8</td><td><strong>Schedule interview</strong></td><td>Click Schedule Interview, fill date/time/panel</td><td>Interview created, status updated</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">4.9</td><td><strong>Send offer letter</strong></td><td>Click Send Offer, fill offer details</td><td>Offer record created, status → Offered</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">4.10</td><td><strong>Add HR note</strong></td><td>Click Add Note, type note</td><td>Note saved, visible on applicant profile</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">4.11</td><td><strong>View status history</strong></td><td>Click status-history on applicant</td><td>Timeline of all status changes displayed</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">4.12</td><td><strong>Recruitment report</strong></td><td>Navigate to /recruitment/compile-report</td><td>Filterable report generated</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr></table><h3>Component 5: Dashboard & Home</h3><table><tr><th class="num">#</th><th style="width:260px">Test Case</th><th>Steps</th><th style="width:280px">Expected Result</th><th class="pf">Pass/Fail</th></tr><tr><td class="num">5.1</td><td><strong>All stats cards load</strong></td><td>Navigate to /dashboard</td><td>8 stat cards: Total Staff, Active Workforce, On Leave, Pending Appraisals, Active Jobs, Total Applicants, Retiring Soon, Pending Leaves</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">5.2</td><td><strong>Active Workforce formula</strong></td><td>Verify displayed value</td><td>Total Staff − Staff Currently On Approved Leave (covering today)</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">5.3</td><td><strong>Charts render</strong></td><td>Check Age bar + Gender doughnut charts</td><td>Both visible, no JS console errors</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">5.4</td><td><strong>Staff Performance DataTable</strong></td><td>Scroll to Staff Performance section</td><td>All staff with appraisal scores descending; Copy/Excel/PDF/Print buttons</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">5.5</td><td><strong>Print Certificate (top scorer)</strong></td><td>Click award icon on #1 ranked employee</td><td>New window with styled certificate, auto-prints</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">5.6</td><td><strong>Notification badge visibility</strong></td><td>Check bell icon badge</td><td>Fully visible (not clipped at top); number matches unread count</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">5.7</td><td><strong>Notification dropdown</strong></td><td>Click bell icon</td><td>Unread notifications list + "Mark all as read"</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">5.8</td><td><strong>Mark one read</strong></td><td>Click a notification item</td><td>Item removed, badge count decrements</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">5.9</td><td><strong>Mark all read</strong></td><td>Click "Mark all as read"</td><td>All items gone, badge hidden, shows "0 unread"</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr></table><h3>Component 6: Staff Registry Directory</h3><table><tr><th class="num">#</th><th style="width:260px">Test Case</th><th>Steps</th><th style="width:280px">Expected Result</th><th class="pf">Pass/Fail</th></tr><tr><td class="num">6.1</td><td><strong>Staff list loads</strong></td><td>Navigate to /staff</td><td>Table with all staff, pagination, filter controls</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">6.2</td><td><strong>Search by name</strong></td><td>Type name in search box</td><td>Table filters in real-time</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">6.3</td><td><strong>Filter by department/status</strong></td><td>Select filters, click Apply</td><td>Results filtered by criteria</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">6.4</td><td><strong>View staff profile</strong></td><td>Click "View" on any row</td><td>Profile page with photo, details, tabbed sections</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">6.5</td><td><strong>Profile tabs switch</strong></td><td>Click each tab: Bio, Academic, Experience, Attachments, Promotions</td><td>Each panel shows correct content, no JS errors</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">6.6</td><td><strong>Edit modal fields</strong></td><td>Click "Modify System Meta Data"</td><td>Modal: Name, Phone, Department (dropdown), Supervisor (dropdown), Access Level (dropdown), Engagement Mode (dropdown)</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">6.7</td><td><strong>Save profile changes</strong></td><td>Change dept/supervisor/role, save</td><td>Green success alert, page reloads, changes persist</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">6.8</td><td><strong>Validation on empty</strong></td><td>Clear Name, submit</td><td>Red error alert, modal stays open</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">6.9</td><td><strong>Download Dossier PDF</strong></td><td>Click "Download Dossier"</td><td>Modal with animated progress bar + percentage → PDF downloads</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">6.10</td><td><strong>Dossier PDF content</strong></td><td>Open downloaded PDF</td><td>Contains: Personal Information, Education, Experience, Promotion tables</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr></table><h3>Component 7: Staff Self-Service Portal</h3><table><tr><th class="num">#</th><th style="width:260px">Test Case</th><th>Steps</th><th style="width:280px">Expected Result</th><th class="pf">Pass/Fail</th></tr><tr><td class="num">7.1</td><td><strong>Portal access</strong></td><td>Login as Staff, go to /staff/portal</td><td>Portal dashboard with links to all self-service features</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">7.2</td><td><strong>Bank details view</strong></td><td>Go to /staff/bank-details</td><td>Form with saved data or empty fields</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">7.3</td><td><strong>Save bank details</strong></td><td>Fill bank name, account, mobile money; submit</td><td>Success message, data persists on reload</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">7.4</td><td><strong>Submit leave request</strong></td><td>Go to /staff/my-leave, fill form, submit</td><td>Leave request created with Pending status</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">7.5</td><td><strong>Leave balance</strong></td><td>Check leave view page</td><td>Entitlement (from rank) minus approved leave used this year</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">7.6</td><td><strong>Submit promotion request</strong></td><td>Go to /staff/promotion, fill form, submit</td><td>Promotion request created with Pending status</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">7.7</td><td><strong>Submit self-appraisal</strong></td><td>Go to /staff/appraisal, fill scores, submit</td><td>Appraisal saved with Pending status</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">7.8</td><td><strong>Payslip view</strong></td><td>Go to /staff/payslips</td><td>Payslip list or "no payslips" message</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">7.9</td><td><strong>Read-only Dossier</strong></td><td>Click "View Full Dossier"</td><td>5 sections: User Account, Personal Info, Education, Experience, Files</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr></table><h3>Component 8: Approvals Workflow</h3><table><tr><th class="num">#</th><th style="width:260px">Test Case</th><th>Steps</th><th style="width:280px">Expected Result</th><th class="pf">Pass/Fail</th></tr><tr><td class="num">8.1</td><td><strong>Approvals dashboard (Supervisor)</strong></td><td>Login as Supervisor, go to /staff/approvals</td><td>Pending leave, promotion, appraisal items for review</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">8.2</td><td><strong>Approve leave (Supervisor)</strong></td><td>Click Approve on pending leave</td><td>Status → Pending HR Approval, HR notified</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">8.3</td><td><strong>Decline leave (Supervisor)</strong></td><td>Click Decline</td><td>Status → Declined, staff notified</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">8.4</td><td><strong>Approve promotion (Supervisor)</strong></td><td>Click Approve</td><td>Status → Pending HR Approval</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">8.5</td><td><strong>Decline promotion (Supervisor)</strong></td><td>Click Decline</td><td>Status → Declined</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">8.6</td><td><strong>Comment on appraisal</strong></td><td>Submit comment</td><td>Status → Commented</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">8.7</td><td><strong>HR final approval (leave)</strong></td><td>Login as HR, check approvals</td><td>Pending HR items visible</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">8.8</td><td><strong>HR approves leave</strong></td><td>HR clicks Approve</td><td>Status → Approved, staff notified</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">8.9</td><td><strong>HR reviews promotion</strong></td><td>HR Approve/Decline + comment</td><td>Status updated, notification created</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr></table><h3>Component 9: Leave Management</h3><table><tr><th class="num">#</th><th style="width:260px">Test Case</th><th>Steps</th><th style="width:280px">Expected Result</th><th class="pf">Pass/Fail</th></tr><tr><td class="num">9.1</td><td><strong>Leave list</strong></td><td>Navigate to /staff/leave</td><td>DataTable, Copy/Excel/PDF/Print buttons</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">9.2</td><td><strong>Create leave (Admin)</strong></td><td>Click "New Leave Request", fill form</td><td>Leave request created</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">9.3</td><td><strong>Date validation</strong></td><td>Set end_date before start_date</td><td>Validation error displayed</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr></table><h3>Component 10: Performance Appraisals</h3><table><tr><th class="num">#</th><th style="width:260px">Test Case</th><th>Steps</th><th style="width:280px">Expected Result</th><th class="pf">Pass/Fail</th></tr><tr><td class="num">10.1</td><td><strong>Appraisal list (Admin)</strong></td><td>Navigate to /staff/appraisals</td><td>DataTable, Copy/Excel/PDF/Print buttons</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">10.2</td><td><strong>Create new appraisal</strong></td><td>Click "New Appraisal", fill metrics and scores</td><td>Appraisal record created</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">10.3</td><td><strong>HR finalizes</strong></td><td>Click "Finalize" on appraisal</td><td>Confirmation modal, appraisal locked</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">10.4</td><td><strong>Appraisal PDF</strong></td><td>Click PDF button</td><td>PDF downloads with scores</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr></table><h3>Component 11: Promotions Management</h3><table><tr><th class="num">#</th><th style="width:260px">Test Case</th><th>Steps</th><th style="width:280px">Expected Result</th><th class="pf">Pass/Fail</th></tr><tr><td class="num">11.1</td><td><strong>Promotion list</strong></td><td>Navigate to /staff/promotions</td><td>DataTable, export buttons</td><td class="pf">☐</td></tr><tr><td class="num">11.2</td><td><strong>Approve/Decline actions</strong></td><td>Check Actions column (Admin